text: Keysher Fuller Spence Keysher Fuller Spence (born 12 July, 1994) is a Costa Rican football player who plays for C.S. Herediano in the Costa Rican Liga FPD. Fuller made his debut for the senior Costa Rica national football team at the Avaya Stadium on 2 February, 2019 against the United States. ==References== Category:Costa Rican footballers Category:Costa Rica international footballers Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Association footballers not categorized by position Category:2019 CONCACAF Gold Cup players
